item.title: Prayer bpn10186 in Māori
item.description: *Ki a koe e rapu nei i te Pono! Mēnā koe e hiahia ana mā Te Atua tō mata e whakakite me koropiko atu, me inoi atu, me tuku atu i tōu reo ki a Ia i te waenganui pō, me kī: Ete Ariki, kua anga kē atu tōku mata ki Tōu aroaro, a, kua ruku kē atu ahau ki te moana o Tōu Aroha. e te Ariki whakamāramatia tōku pōuritanga ki Tōu rama, ā, whakakoangia ahau
